OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWar widows who lost        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpensions to receive        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fcompensation               
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, War widows who were forced to forfeit  
OL,6, their pensions will receive a lump sum 
OL,7, payment after a long-running campaign. 
OL,9,FThe compensation scheme will benefit   
OL,10,Fspouses who lost their government      
OL,11,Fincome if they remarried or moved in   
OL,12,Fwith a new partner before 2015.        
OL,14,FUp to 380 people thought to be affected
OL,15,Fwill receive #87,500, but the          
OL,16,Fgovernment said it is "not possible" to
OL,17,Frestore their pensions in full.        
OL,19,FIt has also been confirmed that the    
OL,20,Fsums paid out will be subject to tax.  
